@startuml sequence_stacks
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Smart Stacks

actor User
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "GET /api/stacks" as API
participant "MemoryCache" as CACHE
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "contacts + embeddings" as DB

User -> UI: load home
UI -> API: GET /api/stacks
API -> CTX: stacks for me
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: rows
loop per stack
    API -> CACHE: get count(userId, stackId)
    alt hit
        CACHE --> API: count
    else miss
        API -> CTX: count contacts by kind
        CTX -> DB: SELECT / semantic search
        DB --> CTX: n
        API -> CACHE: set 5min
    end
end
API --> UI: StackDto[]

User -> UI: tap AI founders card
UI -> UI: navigate /search?stackId=...
UI -> API: GET /api/stacks/:id/contacts
API --> UI: contacts
UI --> User: list of contacts

@enduml
